lead_paragraph: The 80th Masters, which starts on Thursday, shapes up as one of the best in recent memory with world number one Jason Day heading a list of high-profile players in superb form over the past three months.

headline.print_headline: Masters Special in Prospect as Day Tops Stellar Cast
